name: Ginarte O’Dwyer Gonzalez Gallardo & Winograd, LLP

overview:
With over 150 years of combined experience, the attorneys at Ginarte O’Dwyer Gonzalez Gallardo & Winograd, LLP, have been serving clients in Newark, New York City, Perth Amboy, Union City, Elizabeth, Clifton and throughout the New York and New Jersey metro area. Our team of 25 attorneys concentrate on a variety of legal matters including personal injury, workers’ compensation, employment law, family law, social security and general practice matters. This means that we are equipped to provide you with the knowledgeable and professional legal advice you need.

In addition to our skilled attorneys, the Ginarte Law Firm also has an 85-person support staff. Our attorneys and staff are available in six convenient offices, so no matter where you are in the New York or New Jersey metro area, we have a location near you. We offer free no-obligation consultations at all of our offices so you can come in and speak to a legal professional about how we can help you.
